    "translation":{"eng":"All of you come and see! The Vaiṣṇavas, headed by Advaita Ācārya, are dancing along the banks of the Gaṅgā, going from one ghāṭa to the next. At such a sight, the wicked personality Kali falls into great distress and runs for his life."}},{
    "lines":[
